Description:
--------------
Gran Turismo 5 Prologue, is the prologue of Gran Turismo 5. It's a secondary game in the Gran Turismo series. The game is developed by Polyphony Digital and is one of the major games and PlayStation 3 franchise. It is available in two formats: Blu-ray and download on the PlayStation Store. The game was released in Japan on December 13, 2007 (with a downloadable demo on 20th October); for Europe arrived on March 26, 2008. The game features 73 cars (updating to Spec III) including the Ferrari Formula 1 Kimi Raikkonen, 6 tracks and 16 players online.
